# bbgo is a modern cryptocurrency trading bot framework supporting
# Binance / MAX / FTX / OKEx / KuCoin / Kraken exchanges via unified
# adapter interfaces; ships with strategy modules (grid trading, DCA,
# rebalance, pivot-point, harmonic, supertrend, etc.) configured via
# `bbgo.yaml`; backtest engine with historical kline replay; PnL
# calculation; Slack/Telegram notification integration; embedded
# Prometheus metrics server.  CLI invocations follow `bbgo run
# --config bbgo.yaml` pattern for live trading; `bbgo backtest`
# pattern for backtests.  Every flag also reads from environment
# variables via viper's auto-binding (e.g. `BINANCE_API_KEY` env var
# is bound to `--binance-api-key`).
