# arbitrary-precision decimal library is `github.com/shopspring/decimal`
# by Spring Mc — arbitrary-precision fixed-point decimal type with
# configurable scale + rounding modes (banker's / half-up / half-down /
# half-even / ceiling / floor / half-away-from-zero) + JSON/SQL
# marshalling + protobuf encoding.  THE Go answer to "I'm dealing with
# money and can't tolerate float imprecision."  Used by every Go
# cryptocurrency trading bot (bbgo, hummingbot-go-wrapper, ccxt-go),
